body: +1, route generation is broken with spanish translations that have "tilde" characters (á,é,í...)
@bbonamin Can you confirm that it works fine using https://github.com/pcreux/active_admin/tree/patch-issue-799 ?

I changed the reference to the git repo in my Gemfile: `gem 'activeadmin', :git => 'https://github.com/pcreux/active_admin.git'`.

Then I used the command `bundle update activeadmin`

And finally I tried to generate the assets: `rails g active_admin:assets` but the error is still present: https://gist.github.com/1422767

If I remove the tildes from the model translations in my yml file, it works again. Did I miss anything?

Yup! You missed the branch! :)

Add this to the gem file: :branch => "patch-issue-799"

Thanks for testing this!

It works perfectly!
